Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:15.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,160.389)}The Monstrous Girakorogi's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,690.389)}Nails of Death
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what your killer\Nsound waves can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... I'll do the\Nsame thing to you, very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've seen what you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I must put you to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then let me\Nfight the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can fight the Rider any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, you must use your\Nterrifying nails of death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to send all of Japan into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me a combatant\Nwho has outlived his usefulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what your nails of death can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real show is what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite impressive indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see the power of my red nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone pierced by these nails
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,will return to life with these\Nsame red poisoned nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi's nails of death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will spread his mysterious disease\Nthrough the population exponentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They've never even seen a cricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids who've never seen crickets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't help but feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to teach them\Nsome bug-hunting tricks tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When that's over, I'll take\Nthem bug-hunting with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring two kids I know tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My head... my head's splitting in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Girakorogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Girakorogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I won't obey some monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, now. Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Girakorogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down a little, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pacing like a bear in the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wonder where Naoki is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna be late for Sunday class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Naoki's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After Takeshi went to all that trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mitsuru, you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop Naoki off on my motorbike later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late. What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki. That's not nice to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I ended up sleeping late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:06:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go into that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm going to teach you about insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a model of a cricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all bring notebooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See if you can make a good\Ndrawing of this while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Teacher, today's not a drawing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were gonna teach us\Nhow to hunt bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You said you'd teach us\Nhow to hunt bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Teacher! Mr. Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the first victim of my red nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just have to sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna get everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was a roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The children will live only three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In that time, they will spread\Nthe red nails to more and more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better tell Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tachibana Racing Club here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My colleague Ogawa is attacking\Nchildren with a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ogawa guy is working for Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hey, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's red nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd find Shocker here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'll face you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Girakorogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:42.28,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Combatants, you've done enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi... what's your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to kill the combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this... killer sound waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And another blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Girakorogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've almost killed the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... now I'll finish the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He got away... damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost had him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those stupid combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, Mitsuru... forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. Those Shocker bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to use these red\Nnails to throw the city into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally come, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Use Ogawa to lure him into our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa! Ogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... working with Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. I just\Nescaped from Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Base?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come back with me, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where to find the\Nantidote to cure everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Show me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa... is the medicine in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it was a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'll have to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'll break through and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... now a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll jump through that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's great scientists\Nworked hard to create these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorbing mats that absorb\Nany force directed into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use any of your\Nprecious jumps or kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, face my sound waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no absorbing\Nmat on that high window...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could hit that window with\Nmy kick, I could escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a chance now\Nthat will never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Use everything you have\Nto kill the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:46.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:49.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:57.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:01.10,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:19.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:58.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:13.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:41.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! You destroyed my transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Girakorogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your killer sound waves,\Nyou're just like any other monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! They're all back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't that nice?\N- Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the others, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fine, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then untie me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The actions of Hongo\NTakeshi, the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:58.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,kept the city safe from\NShocker's evil plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:04.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker will send more\Nnew cyborgs to attack your city!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.72,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:15.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Elekibotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:18.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A swarm of fireballs burns hot and red.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:20.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When one of them lets out a flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,people catch fire in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Kamen Rider! Beat your foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider in,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:31.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"The Monstrous Elekibotaru's\NFireball Attack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs115\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,725.389)}The Monstrous Elekibotaru's\NFireball Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:40.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:43.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:07.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Girakorogi's\NNails of Death